1 should have been able to discuss this sounding in a much more conclusive way had each 100 fathom , mark been timed. The time is all right by the 500 fathoms, and the sounding appears to be good to the depth of about 2,800 or 3,000 fathoms· After that depth had been reached, the shot probably remained at the bot- tom.
